***Ecaluate: Fact Checking***
Reflection;
asking chatbot are you correct
You can ask a chatbot to fact check some content. It helps to get more than one chatbot’s feedback when fact-checking, and also helps to do some additional research on your own if a chatbot flags something as factually incorrect.

It also helps to explicitly instruct the chatbot to “check the factually accuracy” instead of the more general question “is this correct?”

You can ask a chatbot to fact check its previous completion. You can ask “Are you sure?”


Apps used

