Suggested practice:

Ask a chatbot to fact check some claims about science or medicine. For instance, you can ask a chatbot what it thinks about the claim that “humans only use 10% of their brains.”

EVALUATE***Grading***
GRADER MAY ALSO BE WRONG
o ask a chatbot to grade a student’s solution to a task, first ask the chatbot to work out the solution on its own. Then ask it to compare with the student’s solution. Then decide if the student’s solution is correct. Then, if the student’s solution is incorrect, ask it to give hints.

The chatbot as a grader may get the solution wrong as well, so try more than one chatbot, and also review the results yourself to get an idea of what kinds of questions/problems each chatbot is able to properly grade.


